<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Grace's Chinese Classroom · Learn Chinese in Summer</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Caveat:wght@500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --sky-top:#bfe3f0;
    --sky-mid:#d9edd8;
    --sky-bottom:#f3f8e8;
    --grass-dark:#5f9a52;
    --grass-mid:#82b968;
    --grass-light:#a9d189;
    --sun:#f6d776;
    --sun-glow:#fbe9b0;
    --cream:#fffcf3;
    --ink:#33402f;
    --ink-soft:#5c6b53;
    --brown:#a6743f;
    --brown-dark:#8a5f30;
    --card:#fffef9;
    --shadow: 0 12px 30px -12px rgba(60,80,40,0.25);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    color:var(--ink);
    background:var(--cream);
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  h1,h2,h3,.serif{
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif;
  }
  .accent-hand{
    font-family:'Caveat','Inter',cursive;
  }
  a{color:inherit;}
  img{max-width:100%;display:block;}

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  nav{
    position:fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:100;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:16px 6vw;
    background:rgba(255,252,243,0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(95,154,82,0.15);
  }
  .logo{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight:700; font-size:20px; color:var(--brown-dark);
    text-decoration:none;
  }
  .logo svg{width:28px;height:28px;}
  .nav-links{
    display:flex; gap:28px; list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0;
    font-size:15px; font-weight:500; color:var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .nav-links a{text-decoration:none; position:relative; padding-bottom:2px;}
  .nav-links a::after{
    content:''; position:absolute; left:0; bottom:-3px; width:0; height:2px;
    background:var(--grass-dark); transition:width .25s ease;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover::after{width:100%;}
  .nav-cta{
    background:var(--brown); color:#fff; padding:9px 20px; border-radius:999px;
    font-size:14px; font-weight:500; text-decoration:none; box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  @media(max-width:820px){ .nav-links{display:none;} }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; align-items:center;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--sky-top) 0%, var(--sky-mid) 55%, var(--sky-bottom) 100%);
    overflow:hidden;
    padding-top:80px;
  }
  .sun{
    position:absolute; top:9%; right:14%;
    width:120px; height:120px; border-radius:50%;
    background:radial-gradient(circle, var(--sun) 0%, var(--sun-glow) 55%, rgba(251,233,176,0) 75%);
    filter:blur(0.5px);
  }
  .cloud{
    position:absolute; opacity:.9;
  }
  .cloud svg{width:100%;height:100%;display:block;}
  .cloud-1{ top:14%; left:-10%; width:220px; animation:drift 55s linear infinite; }
  .cloud-2{ top:24%; left:-20%; width:150px; animation:drift 70s linear infinite; animation-delay:-20s; opacity:.75;}
  .cloud-3{ top:8%; left:-15%; width:110px; animation:drift 40s linear infinite; animation-delay:-8s; opacity:.6;}
  @keyframes drift{
    from{ transform:translateX(0); }
    to{ transform:translateX(140vw); }
  }
  .kite{
    position:absolute; top:20%; left:70%; width:46px; opacity:.9;
    animation:float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes float{
    0%,100%{ transform:translateY(0) rotate(-4deg); }
    50%{ transform:translateY(-18px) rotate(4deg); }
  }
  .hero-content{
    position:relative; z-index:5; text-align:center; padding:0 20px;
    max-width:720px;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    font-size:14px; letter-spacing:.08em; color:var(--brown-dark);
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.55); padding:6px 16px; border-radius:999px;
    margin-bottom:22px; border:1px solid rgba(166,116,63,0.25);
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(34px,6vw,58px);
    line-height:1.25; margin:0 0 18px; color:#3c4a30;
    font-weight:700;
  }
  .hero h1 .brush{
    color:var(--brown-dark);
    font-family:'Caveat', cursive; font-size:1.15em; font-weight:600;
  }
  .hero p.lead{
    font-size:17px; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.9; margin:0 auto 34px;
    max-width:520px;
  }
  .hero-btns{ display:flex; gap:16px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .btn-primary, .btn-ghost{
    padding:13px 28px; border-radius:999px; font-size:15px; font-weight:500;
    text-decoration:none; transition:transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
    display:inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary{ background:var(--brown); color:#fff; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
  .btn-primary:hover{ transform:translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-ghost{ background:rgba(255,255,255,.6); color:var(--ink); border:1px solid rgba(95,154,82,.35); }
  .btn-ghost:hover{ background:#fff; }

  /* hill silhouette divider */
  .hill-divider{ position:relative; width:100%; line-height:0; margin-top:-2px; }
  .hill-divider svg{ width:100%; height:auto; display:block; }

  /* grass sway at very bottom of hero */
  .grass-row{
    position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; width:100%; height:90px; z-index:4;
  }
  .grass-row svg{ width:100%; height:100%; }
  .blade{ transform-origin:bottom center; animation:sway 4.5s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes sway{
    0%,100%{ transform:rotate(-3deg); }
    50%{ transform:rotate(3deg); }
  }

  /* ---------- SECTION SHELL ---------- */
  section.block{
    position:relative;
    padding:100px 6vw 120px;
  }
  .band-sky{ background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f3f8e8 0%, #eef7ea 100%); }
  .band-cream{ background:var(--cream); }
  .band-green{ background:linear-gradient(180deg, #eaf4e2 0%, #f7f2e2 100%); }

  .section-head{
    text-align:center; max-width:640px; margin:0 auto 56px;
  }
  .section-tag{
    display:inline-block; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:.12em; color:var(--grass-dark);
    font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px; text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .section-head h2{
    font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,38px); margin:0 0 14px; color:#3c4a30;
  }
  .section-head p{ color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.8; margin:0; font-size:15.5px; }

  /* ---------- ABOUT ---------- */
  .about-wrap{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:280px 1fr; gap:56px; align-items:center;
    max-width:980px; margin:0 auto;
  }
  .about-portrait{
    position:relative; width:100%; aspect-ratio:1/1; border-radius:50%;
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #fff 0%, #fdf3d9 40%, var(--grass-light) 100%);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    border:6px solid #fff;
  }
  .about-portrait svg{ width:78%; }
  .about-text h3{ font-size:26px; margin:0 0 14px; color:#3c4a30; }
  .about-text p{ color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.95; font-size:15.5px; margin:0 0 14px; }
  .about-tags{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:20px; }
  .about-tags span{
    background:#fff; border:1px solid rgba(95,154,82,.3); color:var(--grass-dark);
    padding:6px 14px; border-radius:999px; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:500;
  }
  @media(max-width:760px){ .about-wrap{ grid-template-columns:1fr; text-align:center; }
    .about-portrait{ width:220px; margin:0 auto; } .about-tags{justify-content:center;} }

  /* ---------- LEVEL SECTIONS ---------- */
  .level-header{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:12px;
  }
  .level-badge{
    width:46px; height:46px; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-weight:700; color:#fff; font-size:18px;
  }
  .badge-beginner{ background:var(--grass-mid); }
  .badge-advanced{ background:var(--brown); }

  .card-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:22px;
    max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto;
  }
  @media(max-width:980px){ .card-grid{ grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); } }
  @media(max-width:560px){ .card-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; } }

  .card{
    background:var(--card); border-radius:20px; padding:28px 22px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow); border:1px solid rgba(95,154,82,.12);
    transition:transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
    opacity:0; transform:translateY(24px);
  }
  .card.in-view{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  .card:hover{ transform:translateY(-6px); box-shadow:0 18px 34px -14px rgba(60,80,40,.32); }
  .card .icon-wrap{
    width:56px; height:56px; border-radius:16px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .card h4{ margin:0 0 8px; font-size:17px; font-family:'Fraunces',serif; color:#3c4a30; }
  .card p{ margin:0 0 16px; font-size:13.8px; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.7; }
  .card .card-link{
    font-size:13.5px; font-weight:600; color:var(--brown-dark); text-decoration:none;
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:5px;
  }
  .card .card-link::after{ content:'→'; transition:transform .2s ease; }
  .card .card-link:hover::after{ transform:translateX(4px); }

  .icon-yellow{ background:#fdf0c8; }
  .icon-green{ background:#dcefd0; }
  .icon-blue{ background:#d8ecf2; }
  .icon-brown{ background:#f0e0c9; }

  /* ---------- STUDENT WORK ---------- */
  .gallery{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:18px; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto;
  }
  @media(max-width:900px){ .gallery{ grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);} }
  .gallery-item{
    position:relative; border-radius:18px; overflow:hidden; aspect-ratio:4/5;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .gallery-item .ph{
    width:100%; height:100%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .gallery-item .cap{
    position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; padding:14px 16px 12px;
    background:linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(50,60,40,.72), rgba(50,60,40,0));
    color:#fff; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:500;
  }

  /* ---------- CTA / CONTACT ---------- */
  .cta-block{
    position:relative; text-align:center; padding:100px 6vw 120px;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, #eef7ea 0%, #cfe8c6 100%);
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .cta-block .inner{ position:relative; z-index:3; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; }
  .cta-block h2{ font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,36px); margin:0 0 16px; color:#33402f; }
  .cta-block p{ color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.9; margin:0 0 32px; font-size:15.5px; }

  footer{
    background:#3c4a30; color:#e7ecdf; padding:44px 6vw 30px; text-align:center;
    font-size:13.5px;
  }
  footer .foot-logo{ font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-size:18px; margin-bottom:10px; }
  footer .foot-links{ display:flex; gap:24px; justify-content:center; margin:16px 0; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  footer a{ text-decoration:none; color:#dfe6d3; }
  footer .copyright{ opacity:.6; margin-top:18px; }

  /* ---------- JOURNEY (scroll narrative) ---------- */
  .journey-track{
    position:relative; max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; padding-left:44px;
  }
  .journey-line{
    position:absolute; left:9px; top:6px; bottom:20px; width:2px;
    background:rgba(95,154,82,.22);
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .journey-line-fill{
    width:100%; height:0%;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--grass-mid), var(--sun));
    transition:height .5s ease;
  }
  .journey-item{
    position:relative; padding-bottom:60px;
    opacity:0; transform:translateY(22px);
    transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease;
  }
  .journey-item:last-child{ padding-bottom:4px; }
  .journey-item.in-view{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  .journey-dot{
    position:absolute; left:-44px; top:5px; width:14px; height:14px; border-radius:50%;
    background:#fff; border:3px solid var(--grass-mid);
    transition:background .3s ease, border-color .3s ease;
  }
  .journey-item.in-view .journey-dot{ background:var(--brown); border-color:var(--brown); }
  .journey-stage{
    font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.1em; color:var(--brown-dark); font-weight:600;
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .journey-item h3{
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-size:clamp(21px,3vw,29px);
    margin:10px 0 12px; color:#3c4a30; line-height:1.45; font-weight:600;
  }
  .journey-item p{
    color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.9; font-size:15px; margin:0; max-width:560px;
  }
  @media(max-width:600px){
    .journey-track{ padding-left:34px; }
    .journey-dot{ left:-34px; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    .cloud-1,.cloud-2,.cloud-3,.kite,.blade{ animation:none !important; }
    .card{ opacity:1; transform:none; }
    .journey-item{ opacity:1; transform:none; }
  }

  /* ---------- LOGO RIGHT-CLICK MENU ---------- */
  .logo{ position:relative; user-select:none; }

  .rcl-menu{
    position:fixed; z-index:999;
    min-width:230px;
    background:var(--cream);
    border:1px solid rgba(95,154,82,.25);
    border-radius:16px;
    box-shadow:0 20px 40px -14px rgba(50,60,40,.35);
    padding:8px;
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    opacity:0; transform:scale(.96) translateY(-4px);
    pointer-events:none;
    transition:opacity .14s ease, transform .14s ease;
  }
  .rcl-menu.open{ opacity:1; transform:scale(1) translateY(0); pointer-events:auto; }

  .rcl-title{
    font-size:11.5px; letter-spacing:.06em; color:var(--ink-soft);
    padding:8px 12px 6px; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:600;
  }
  .rcl-item{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    width:100%; text-align:left; background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer;
    padding:9px 12px; border-radius:10px;
    font-size:14px; color:var(--ink); font-family:inherit;
  }
  .rcl-item:hover, .rcl-item:focus-visible{ background:#eef4e6; outline:none; }
  .rcl-item svg{ width:16px; height:16px; flex-shrink:0; color:var(--grass-dark); }
  .rcl-item .rcl-check{ margin-left:auto; opacity:0; color:var(--grass-dark); font-size:12px; }
  .rcl-item.copied .rcl-check{ opacity:1; }

  .rcl-sep{ height:1px; background:rgba(95,154,82,.18); margin:6px 8px; }

  .rcl-palette{ display:flex; gap:8px; padding:8px 12px 10px; }
  .rcl-swatch{
    width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:9px; cursor:pointer; border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    position:relative; flex-shrink:0;
    transition:transform .15s ease;
  }
  .rcl-swatch:hover{ transform:translateY(-3px); }
  .rcl-swatch::after{
    content:attr(data-label); position:absolute; bottom:-22px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%);
    font-size:10px; white-space:nowrap; color:var(--ink-soft); opacity:0; transition:opacity .15s ease;
  }
  .rcl-swatch:hover::after{ opacity:1; }

  .rcl-hint{
    position:absolute; top:100%; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(4px);
    font-size:11px; color:var(--ink-soft); background:#fff; padding:3px 9px; border-radius:999px;
    white-space:nowrap; opacity:0; pointer-events:none; transition:opacity .18s ease;
    box-shadow:0 6px 14px -6px rgba(50,60,40,.3);
  }
  .logo:hover .rcl-hint{ opacity:.9; }
  @media(max-width:820px){ .rcl-hint{ display:none; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#top" class="logo" data-rcl-logo>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 3C9 7 6 9 6 13a6 6 0 0012 0c0-4-3-6-6-10z" fill="#82b968"/><path d="M12 6c-1.8 2.7-3.6 4.2-3.6 6.8A3.6 3.6 0 0012 16.4" stroke="#5f9a52" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
    Grace's Chinese Classroom
    <span class="rcl-hint">Right-click to copy / download logo</span>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About Me</a></li>
    <li><a href="#journey">My Journey</a></li>
    <li><a href="#beginner">Beginner Chinese</a></li>
    <li><a href="#advanced">Advanced Chinese</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gallery">Student Work</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Online Classes</a>
</nav>

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<header class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="sun"></div>

  <div class="cloud cloud-1"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 90"><ellipse cx="55" cy="55" rx="55" ry="32" fill="#fff"/><ellipse cx="110" cy="40" rx="45" ry="38" fill="#fff"/><ellipse cx="150" cy="58" rx="40" ry="26" fill="#fff"/></svg></div>
  <div class="cloud cloud-2"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 90"><ellipse cx="55" cy="55" rx="55" ry="32" fill="#fff"/><ellipse cx="110" cy="40" rx="45" ry="38" fill="#fff"/><ellipse cx="150" cy="58" rx="40" ry="26" fill="#fff"/></svg></div>
  <div class="cloud cloud-3"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 90"><ellipse cx="55" cy="55" rx="55" ry="32" fill="#fff"/><ellipse cx="110" cy="40" rx="45" ry="38" fill="#fff"/><ellipse cx="150" cy="58" rx="40" ry="26" fill="#fff"/></svg></div>

  <svg class="kite" viewBox="0 0 40 60" fill="none"><path d="M20 2 L36 26 L20 50 L4 26 Z" fill="#f2a65a" stroke="#c9773a" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M20 50 Q22 55 18 60" stroke="#c9773a" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="eyebrow">🌿 Welcome to a summer Chinese classroom</span>
    <h1>Hi, I'm <span class="brush">Grace</span><br>Let's learn Chinese through stories and play</h1>
    <p class="lead">Here you'll find the slides, worksheets, activities and mini games I use in class, plus a little corner for the work my students and I have made together. Take your time — it's a bit like wandering through a summer hillside.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#beginner" class="btn-primary">Browse Teaching Resources</a>
      <a href="#about" class="btn-ghost">Meet Grace</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grass-row">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 90" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,90 L0,40 Q60,10 120,40 Q180,60 240,35 Q300,15 360,42 Q420,65 480,38 Q540,12 600,40 Q660,62 720,36 Q780,14 840,42 Q900,64 960,38 Q1020,12 1080,40 Q1140,60 1200,36 Q1300,14 1440,40 L1440,90 Z" fill="var(--grass-light)" opacity="0.55"/>
      <path d="M0,90 L0,55 Q80,30 160,55 Q240,75 320,50 Q400,28 480,55 Q560,78 640,52 Q720,30 800,56 Q880,76 960,50 Q1040,28 1120,54 Q1220,74 1440,55 L1440,90 Z" fill="var(--grass-mid)"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="hill-divider">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 140" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,90 Q360,20 720,80 Q1080,140 1440,60 L1440,140 L0,140 Z" fill="#eef7ea"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ============ ABOUT ============ -->
<section class="block band-sky" id="about">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="section-tag">About Grace</span>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="about-portrait">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100">
        <circle cx="50" cy="42" r="24" fill="#fbe3c2"/>
        <path d="M26 40 Q26 14 50 14 Q74 14 74 40 Q74 30 60 26 Q50 34 36 26 Q26 30 26 40Z" fill="#5b4636"/>
        <circle cx="41" cy="44" r="2.2" fill="#4a3b2c"/>
        <circle cx="59" cy="44" r="2.2" fill="#4a3b2c"/>
        <path d="M42 54 Q50 60 58 54" stroke="#c17a5a" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M18 92 Q22 62 50 62 Q78 62 82 92 Z" fill="#82b968"/>
        <path d="M32 66 Q50 74 68 66" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity=".6"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <h3>Teacher Grace</h3>
      <p>Hi, I'm Grace, a Chinese teacher. I believe the best way into a language is through stories, play and hands-on activities — not rote memorization. This site is where I've organized the materials I use in class, so I can share them with my students easily, and hopefully one day welcome online learners too.</p>
      <p>Whether you're just starting out with pinyin or already reading short passages and keeping a journal, you'll find something here for you.</p>
      <div class="about-tags">
        <span>🎓 Chinese Teaching</span>
        <span>📖 Beginner · Advanced</span>
        <span>🎮 Interactive Learning</span>
        <span>💻 Online Classes Coming Soon</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
